<<set_left RenN>>

<<enter_right>>

<<highlight right>>
<<set_right DoctorU>>
Doctor: Ah, Doctor Johan! These days have been quite hard haven't they..? 
<<set_right DoctorN>>
Doctor: The number of patients just won't drop, what in the world is happening out there.

-> Ah.. that seems to be the case.
    <<highlight left>>
    Johan (Ren): Ah.. that seems to be the case.
    
    <<highlight right>>
    Doctor: Hm.. There's just no rest for us, is there?
    
-> What exactly is happening out there?
    <<highlight left>>
    Johan (Ren): What exactly is happening out there?
    
    <<highlight right>>
    Doctor: Huh? Don't tell me you have started forgetting stuff, you should really take a rest. 
    Doctor: The protestors turned violent when their leader was shot.
    
    <<highlight left>>
    Johan (Ren): Ah right.

<<highlight right>>
Doctor: The Mayor is out there dealing with the protestors. I seriously can't understand this.
Doctor: Why would a crucial political figure put himself in danger like that? Plus he's funding our hospital!
Doctor: He's the reason why our hospital has such a good reputation!
Doctor: Anyways we should get ready. The break's almost over.

<<exit_left>>
<<exit_right>>
<<complete_objective junior>>
