<<set_left RenN>>

<<highlight right>>
Doctor (Background): Huh? How did you enter in here?!
Doctor (Background): We are about to perform a surgery!
Doctor (Background): What? The Mayor needs immediate attention as well?
Doctor: Hmm.. In that case, Quick Johan, we have to save the Mayor.

<<highlight left>>
Johan (Ren): Huh? But what about the child?

<<highlight right>>
Doctor: Dont you understand? If the Mayor dies, so does our reputation!
Doctor: We can't afford to let someone as important as him die in our hospital just because of a patient queue.
Doctor: We MUST save him.

-> Save the Child
    <<highlight both>>
